scenes.title: Fuego Fortress
scenes.description: Fuego Fortress is Nikki Fuego's 2023 Game Jam submission. In this scene Nikki used AI for every single texture, skybox, NPC dialogue, NPC style concepts, and maze layout on each floor. This entire scene was made in SDK7 with the Visual Studio SDK7 Editor Extension. This is an 8x8 estate. The entirity of this scene was made during the Game Jam duration; nothing here was reused from previous projects. In this lucid dream you journey through the Fortress to discover your true identity and purpose in this universe.

scenes.title: Soul Magic
scenes.description: Soul Magic is a magic fantasy role play game and the story surrounds the magic school of Elswyth. Collect ores and magic stones from mining, farming plants and discover through digging. You can also trade resources for Gold Midas, the currency in the world. Soul can be recovered from meditation and will be consumed while conducting activities. We are now running the Admission Carnival. Players who pass the admission quiz will be awarded the Sunstaff, a magic staff that gives you the ability to cast spells!
